---
import SectionHeader from "../SectionHeader.astro";
import FAQItem from "../FAQItem.astro";
---

<section id="faq" class="w-full bg-bg-cards">
<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-12 py-16 lg:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-[120px] max-w-[1440px] mx-auto">
  <SectionHeader
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    subtitle="We know reaching out can feel like a big step. Here are answers to the questions we hear most."
  />
  <div class="flex flex-col w-full max-w-[680px]">

    <FAQItem
      question="What is InnerMind Solutions?"
      answer="InnerMind Solutions is an Psychology services organisation, offering choice-centred counselling and development practice grounded in Choice Theory and Reality Therapy. We support individuals, institutions, and organisations in building clarity, responsible choice, and meaningful growth."
    />
    <FAQItem
      question="What is Choice Theory and Reality Therapy?"
      answer="Founded by Dr.William Glasser, Choice Theory explains how our needs influence the choices we make. Reality Therapy is a counselling technique that helps individuals take responsibility for present behaviour and move toward more effective action."
    />
    <FAQItem
      question="How is your approach different from traditional counseling?"
      answer="Our work focuses on responsible choice rather than blame. We emphasise present behaviour, self-direction, and practical change rather than only exploring past events."
    />
    <FAQItem
      question="Is counselling confidential?"
      answer="Yes. All individual sessions are confidential and follow professional ethical standards. Corporate engagements maintain strict boundaries between personal information and organisational reporting."
    />
    <FAQItem
      question="What happens in a typical counselling session?"
      answer="It is a structured talk therapy that uses tailored, interactive sessions to help individuals tackle personal challenges. Its primary objective is to empower the person to achieve their desired life changes."
    />
    <FAQItem
      question="How do I get started?"
      answer="You can begin by sharing your details through our intake form. We will connect with you to understand your needs and guide you toward the right support."
    />
